<ListItem><Paragraph Foreground="{DynamicResource ColorBrush1}"><Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E9%87%91%E7%9F%BF%E7%9F%B3" Margin="0,0,0,-8">金矿石</local:MyTextButton></Underline>会以矿团的形式生成于<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" Margin="0,0,0,-8">主世界</local:MyTextButton></Underline>高度为Y=-64至32的石头之间，也会生成在<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E6%81%B6%E5%9C%B0" Margin="0,0,0,-8">恶地</local:MyTextButton></Underline>、<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E7%96%8F%E6%9E%97%E6%81%B6%E5%9C%B0" Margin="0,0,0,-8">疏林恶地</local:MyTextButton></Underline>和<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E9%A3%8E%E8%9A%80%E6%81%B6%E5%9C%B0" Margin="0,0,0,-8">风蚀恶地</local:MyTextButton></Underline>的Y=28至256高度处。</Paragraph></ListItem>
