<ListItem><Paragraph Foreground="{DynamicResource ColorBrush1}"><Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E9%87%91%E7%9F%BF%E7%9F%B3" Margin="0,0,0,-8">金矿石</local:MyTextButton></Underline>和深层<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E9%87%91%E7%9F%BF%E7%9F%B3" Margin="0,0,0,-8">金矿石</local:MyTextButton></Underline>需要铁镐或品质更好的镐来挖掘。</Paragraph></ListItem>
